.000Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2022-07-02T03:27:41.000Z\"}},\"8\":{\"exercise_id\":62,\"exercise_name\":\"Calf Raises- Bilateral\",\"exercise_reps\":15,\"exercise_holds\":\"0\",\"exercise_sets\":2,\"exercise_rests\":\"30\",\"exercise_body_part_id\":10,\"exercise_video_id\":76,\"exercise_instruction_id\":71,\"isActive\":1,\"created_at\":\"2022-07-05T11:10:45.000Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2022-07-05T11:10:45.000Z\",\"exercise_time\":0,\"isMultidirectional\":0,\"isTimeControlled\":0,\"instruction_name\":\"Calf raises- Bilateral\",\"body_part_name\":\"ANKLE & FOOT\",\"video_name\":\"Calf raises- Bilateral\",\"exercise_note\":\"With 4kg weight in hand\",\"exercise_days\":-6.1432891666666665,\"start_date\":\"2022-07-29\",\"end_date\":\"2022-07-29\",\"audioFilePath\":\"/uploads/audios/zian_kopty@dentsu_com_Calf Raises- Bilateral_July_29_2022_audio.mp3\",\"videoObj\":{\"video_id\":76,\"video_name\":\"Calf raises- Bilateral\",\"video_type\":\"exercise\",\"video_youtube_id\":\"IBkNRLeikbc\",\"isActive\":1,\"created_at\":\"2022-07-05T11:08:22.000Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2022-07-05T11:08:22.000Z\",\"id\":1},\"instructionObj\":{\"instruction_id\":71,\"instruction_name\":\"Calf raises- Bilateral\",\"instruction_type\":\"exercise\",\"instruction_description_hindi\":\"{\\\"0\\\":\\\"सहारा लेने के लिए एक दीवार के खिलाफ खड़े हो जाओ। अपने पैरों को अपने नितंब के नीचे रखें।\\\",\\\"1\\\":\\\"अपनी एड़ीयों को ऊपर की ओर उठाएं ताकि पूरा शरीर एक सीधी दिशा में ऊपर की ओर बढ़े न कि आगे की ओर।\\\",\\\"2\\\":\\\"पिंडली की मांसपेशियों को सबसे ऊँचे स्तर पर अधिक कस लें।\\\"}\",\"instruction_description_english\":\"{\\\"0\\\":\\\"Stand against a wall taking support for balance. Keep your feet below your hips.\\\",\\\"1\\\":\\\"Lift your heels upwards so that entire body moves up in a straight direction and not forwards.\\\",\\\"2\\\":\\\"Squeeze and tighten the calves at the highest point.\\\"}\",\"instruction_description_marathi\":null,\"isActive\":1,\"created_at\":\"2022-07-05T03:59:45.000Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2022