.000Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2022-07-08T07:32:11.000Z\",\"id\":1},\"instructionObj\":{\"instruction_id\":173,\"instruction_name\":\"Latissimus stretch\",\"instruction_type\":\"exercise\",\"instruction_description_hindi\":\"{\\\"0\\\":\\\"जिस तरफ आप खिंचाव करना चाहते हैं, उसके विपरीत तरफ दीवार हो ऐसे खड़े हों जाये। \\\",\\\"1\\\":\\\"खिंचाव देने वाले बाजू के हाथ को अपने सिर के ऊपर उठाएं और इसे दीवार की ओर मोड़ें ताकि हाथ दीवार को छुए। \\\",\\\"2\\\":\\\"खिंचाव को बढ़ाने के लिए उसी बाजू वाले पैर को पीछे और तिरछे दूसरे पार अंदर की तरफ ले जाएं। यह स्थिति पकड़कर रखें।\\\"}\",\"instruction_description_english\":\"{\\\"0\\\":\\\"Stand with wall opposite to the side you want to stretch.\\\",\\\"1\\\":\\\"Raise same side arm over your head and take it bend towards the wall so that the hand touches the wall.\\\",\\\"2\\\":\\\"To increase the stretch, take the same side leg behind and inwards crossing the other leg. Hold this position.\\\"}\",\"instruction_description_marathi\":null,\"isActive\":1,\"created_at\":\"2022-07-08T05:35:20.000Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2022-07-08T05:35:20.000Z\"}},\"2\":{\"exercise_id\":246,\"exercise_name\":\"Slump stretch\",\"exercise_reps\":\"5\",\"exercise_holds\":\"0\",\"exercise_sets\":\"4\",\"exercise_rests\":\"10\",\"exercise_body_part_id\":7,\"exercise_video_id\":258,\"exercise_instruction_id\":294,\"isActive\":1,\"created_at\":\"2022-07-14T23:51:18.000Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2022-07-14T23:51:18.000Z\",\"exercise_time\":0,\"isMultidirectional\":0,\"isTimeControlled\":0,\"instruction_name\":\"Slump stretch\",\"body_part_name\":\"LOW BACK & FLANK\",\"video_name\":\"Slump stretch\",\"exercise_note\":\"5 reps alternate sides\",\"exercise_days\":7,\"start_date\":\"2022-08-27\",\"end_date\":\"2022-08-27\",\"audioFilePath\":\"/uploads/audios/prakash_date2003@yahoo_com_Slump stretch_August_27_2022_audio.mp3\",\"videoObj\":{\"video_id\":258,\"video_name\":\"Slump stretch\",\"video_type\":\"exercise\",\"video_youtube_id\":\"5kkpfQGncMI\",\"isActive\":1,\"created_at\":\"2022-07-14T23:44:28.000Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2022-07-14T23:44:28.000Z\",\"id\":1},\"instructionObj\":{\"instruction_id\":294,\"instruction_name\":\"Slump stretch\",\"instruction_type\":\"exercise\",\"instruction_description_hindi\":\"{\\\"0\\\":\\\"एक कुर्सी/बिस्तर के किनारे पर बैठें। इस क्रम का पालन करते हुए प्रारंभिक स्थिति में आएं-\\\",\\\"1\\\":\\\"i) अपने दोनों हाथों को पीठ के निचले हिस्से के पीछे पकड़ें। \\\",\\\"2\\\":\\\"ii) अपनी पीठ को ढीला छोड़कर हल्का आगे मोड़े।\\\",\\\"3\\\":\\\"iii) गर्दन को छाती की ओर मोड़े।\\\",\\\"4\\\":\\\"iv) अपने टखने को छत की ओर खींचे।\\\",\\\"5\\\":\\\"v) अपने घुटने को सीधा करें।\\\"}\",\"instruction_description_english\":\"{\\\"0\\\":\\\"Sit on a chair/edge of the bed. Come in starting position by following this order-\\\",\\\"1\\\":\\\"i) Hold both your hands behind the lower back.\\\",\\\"2\\\":\\\"ii) Slouch your back.\\\",\\\"3\\\":\\\"iii) Touch your chin to chest.\\\",\\\"4\\\":\\\"iv) Pull up your ankle towards the ceiling.\\\",\\\"5\\\":\\\"v) Straighten your knee.\\\"}\",\"instruction_description_marathi\":null,\"isActive\":1,\"created_at\":\"2022-07-14T23:38:55.000Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2022-07-14T23:38:55.000Z\"}},\"3\":{\"exercise_id\":79,\"exercise_name\":\"Figure 4 stretch\",\"exercise_reps\":1,\"exercise_holds\":20,\"exercise_sets\":\"4\",\"exercise_rests\":\"5\",\"exercise_body_part_id\":8,\"exercise_video_id\":83,\"exercise_instruction_id\":106,\"isActive\":1,\"created_at\":\"2022-07-05T21:46:25.000Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2022-07-05T21:46:25.000Z\",\"exercise_time\":0,\"isMultidirectional\":0,\"isTimeControlled\":0,\"instruction_name\":\"Figure 4 stretch\",\"body_part_name\":\"HIP\",\"video_name\":\"Figure 4 stretch\",\"exercise_note\":\"2 reps each side (alternate)\",\"exercise_days\":7,\"start_date\":\"2022-08-27\",\"end_date\":\"2022-08-27\",\"audioFilePath\":\"/uploads/audios/prakash_date2003@yahoo_com_Figure 4 stretch_August_27_2022_audio.mp3\",\"videoObj\":{\"video_id\":83,\"video_name\":\"Figure 4 stretch\",\"video_type\":\"exercise\",\"video_youtube_id\":\"VyVnUS6qEDk\",\"isActive\":1,\"created_at\":\"2022-07-05T21:26:38.000Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2022-07-05T21:26:38.000Z\",\"id\":1},\"instructionObj\":{\"instruction_id\":106,\"instruction_name\":\"Figure 4 stretch\",\"instruction_type\":\"exercise\",\"instruction_description_hindi\":\"{\\\"0\\\":\\\"दोनों घुटनों को मोड़कर पीठ के बल लेट जाएं।\\\",\\\"1\\\":\\\"जिस पैर को व्यायाम करना हो उसे घुमाएँ और दूसरे पैर के ऊपर रखें (जैसे पैरों से ४ अंक बना रहे हो) ।\\\",\\\"2\\\":\\\"दूसरे पैर की जांघ को पकड़कर छाती की तरफ खींचें।\\\",\\\"3\\\":\\\"ऐसा करते समय अपनी कोहनी से घुमाए गए पैर को और अधिक धक्का दें।\\\"}\",\"instruction_description_english\":\"{\\\"0\\\":\\\"Lie down on your back with both knees bent.\\\",\\\"1\\\":\\\"Rotate and keep the targeted side leg on top of the other (like in a figure 4 position).\\\",\\\"2\\\":\\\"Hold your thigh of the other leg and pull it towards your chest.\\\",\\\"3\\\":\\\"While doing so push out the rotated leg more with your elbow.\\\"}\",\"instruction_description_marathi\":null,\"isActive\":1,\"created_at\":\"2022-07-05T21:06:12.000Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2022-07-05T21:06:12.000Z\"}},\"4\":{\"exercise_id\":118,\"exercise_name\":\"Hip flexor stretch- Half kneeling position\",\"exercise_reps\":1,\"exercise_holds\":20,\"exercise_sets\":\"4\",\"exercise_rests\":\"15\",\"exercise_body_part_id\":8,\"exercise_video_id\":123,\"exercise_instruction_id\":147,\"isActive\":1,\"created_at\":\"2022-07-07T01:58:52.000Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2022-07-07T01:58:52.000Z\",\"exercise_time\":0,\"isMultidirectional\":0,\"isTimeControlled\":0,\"instruction_name\":\"Hip flexor stretch- Half kneeling position\",\"body_part_name\":\"HIP\",\"video_name\":\"Hip Flexor stretch- Kneeling position\",\"exercise_note\":\"2 reps each side (alternate)\",\"exercise_days\":7,\"start_date\":\"2022-08-27\",\"end_date\":\"2022-08-27\",\"audioFilePath\":\"/uploads/audios/prakash_date2003@yahoo_com_Hip flexor stretch- Half kneeling 