ees bent.\\\",\\\"1\\\":\\\"Rotate and keep the targeted side leg on top of the other (like in a figure 4 position).\\\",\\\"2\\\":\\\"Hold your thigh of the other leg and pull it towards your chest.\\\",\\\"3\\\":\\\"While doing so push out the rotated leg more with your elbow.\\\"}\",\"instruction_description_marathi\":null,\"isActive\":1,\"created_at\":\"2022-07-05T21:06:12.000Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2022-07-05T21:06:12.000Z\"}},\"3\":{\"exercise_id\":103,\"exercise_name\":\"Hamstring stretch with pelvic tilts in standing\",\"exercise_reps\":15,\"exercise_holds\":0,\"exercise_sets\":2,\"exercise_rests\":30,\"exercise_body_part_id\":9,\"exercise_video_id\":107,\"exercise_instruction_id\":135,\"isActive\":1,\"created_at\":\"2022-07-06T09:50:26.000Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2022-07-06T09:50:26.000Z\",\"exercise_time\":0,\"isMultidirectional\":0,\"isTimeControlled\":0,\"instruction_name\":\"Hamstring stretch with pelvic tilts in standing\",\"body_part_name\":\"KNEE\",\"video_name\":\"Hamstring stretch standing with pelvic tilt\",\"exercise_days\":7,\"start_date\":\"2022-09-13\",\"end_date\":\"2022-09-13\",\"audioFilePath\":\"/uploads/audios/Raviratanpal@gmail_com_Hamstring stretch with pelvic tilts in standing_September_13_2022_audio.mp3\",\"videoObj\":{\"video_id\":107,\"video_name\":\"Hamstring stretch standing with pelvic tilt\",\"video_type\":\"exercise\",\"video_youtube_id\":\"DzlYppcrK3E\",\"isActive\":1,\"created_at\":\"2022-07-06T09:35:04.000Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2022-07-06T09:35:04.000Z\",\"id\":1},\"instructionObj\":{\"instruction_id\":135,\"instruction_name\":\"Hamstring stretch with pelvic tilts in standing\",\"instruction_type\":\"exercise\",\"instruction_description_hindi\":\"{\\\"0\\\":\\\"एक स्टेपर/स्टूल/कम ऊंचाई की कुर्सी पर अपने व्यायाम करनेवाले पैर को रखकर, आपके घुटने सीधे और टखने ढीले रखकर सीधे खड़े हो जाएं।\\\",\\\"1\\\":\\\"अपने नितंबों को पीछे धकेलते हुए अपनी पीठ के निचले हिस्से को तब तक मोड़ें जब तक कि आप अपनी जांघ के पिछले हिस्से में एक आरामदायक खिंचाव