ame if possible or then relax.\\\",\\\"6\\\":\\\"Breathe normally for a few times and repeat the exercise.\\\"}\",\"instruction_description_marathi\":null,\"isActive\":1,\"created_at\":\"2022-08-14T04:43:22.000Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2022-08-14T04:43:22.000Z\"}}}', 1, '2022-10-19 07:32:18', '2022-10-19 07:32:18', '{\"patient_name\":\"manish pal\",\"patient_age\":\"25\",\"patient_gender\":\"M\",\"patient_email\":\"manishpal734@gmail.com\",\"patient_id\":53}', '{\"scale_id\":50,\"scale_name\":\"12-Item Short Form Survey (SF-12)\",\"scale_link\":\"https://orthotoolkit.com/sf-12/\",\"isActive\":1,\"created_At\":\"2022-07-06T23:03:03.000Z\",\"updated_At\":\"2022-07-06T23:03:03.000Z\",\"id\":18,\"ScaleDays\":\"\"}', 'http://13.127.138.88:3000/Prescription?prescription_id=96', '2022-10-26', '', NULL, NULL),
