with seated leg lifts\",\"instruction_type\":\"exercise\",\"instruction_description_hindi\":\"{\\\"0\\\":\\\"पैर फैलाकर बैठने की स्थिति में आएं। \\\",\\\"1\\\":\\\"अपने टखने के पास एक बाधा के रूप में एक वास्तु रखें जिसकी ऊंचाई थेरेपिस्ट की सलाह के अनुसार हों। \\\",\\\"2\\\":\\\"जांघ के सामने की मांसपेशियों को कस लें। \\\",\\\"3\\\":\\\"अपने घुटने को मोड़े बिना, अपने पैर को नितंब से बग़ल में उठाते हुए बाधा को पार करें।\\\"}\",\"instruction_description_english\":\"{\\\"0\\\":\\\"Come in a long sitting position.\\\",\\\"1\\\":\\\"Keep some object with height as advised by therapist, as an obstacle near your ankle.\\\",\\\"2\\\":\\\"Tighten your muscles in front of the thigh.\\\",\\\"3\\\":\\\"Without letting your knee bend, lift your leg from the hip and cross the obstacle sideways.\\\"}\",\"instruction_description_marathi\":null,\"isActive\":1,\"created_at\":\"2022-07-12T01:58:21.000Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2022-07-12T01:58:21.000Z\"}},\"2\":{\"exercise_id\":300,\"exercise_name\":\"VMO strengthening- Supine\",\"exercise_reps\":10,\"exercise_holds\":5,\"exercise_sets\":2,\"exercise_rests\":30,\"exercise_body_part_id\":9,\"exercise_video_id\":315,\"exercise_instruction_id\":347,\"isActive\":1,\"created_at\":\"2022-07-19T04:20:20.000Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2022-07-19T04:20:20.000Z\",\"exercise_time\":0,\"isMultidirectional\":0,\"isTimeControlled\":0,\"instruction_name\":\"VMO strengthening- Supine\",\"body_part_name\":\"KNEE\",\"video_name\":\"VMO strengthening- Supine\",\"exercise_days\":29,\"start_date\":\"2022-11-06\",\"end_date\":\"2022-11-06\",\"audioFilePath\":\"/uploads/audios/vedangv7@gmail_com_VMO strengthening- Supine_November_06_2022_audio.mp3\",\"videoObj\":{\"video_id\":315,\"video_name\":\"VMO strengthening- Supine\",\"video_type\":\"exercise\",\"video_youtube_id\":\"b23BbZl8Pak\",\"isActive\":1,\"created_at\":\"2022-07-19T04:12:53.000Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2022-07-19T04:12:53.000Z\",\"id\":1},\"instructionObj\":{\"instruction_id\":347,\"instruction_name\":\"VMO strengthening- Supine\",\"instruction_type\":\"exercise\",\"instruction_description_hindi\":\"{\\\"0\\\":\\\"जिस पैर का व्यायाम करना हो उसके घुटने के नीचे एक मुड़ा हुआ तकिया/रोलर के साथ लेटें। \\\",\\\"1\\\":\\\"अपनी जांघ के सामने की मांसपेशियों को कस लें, अपने घुटने को नीचे दबाए और आपकी एड़ी को जमीन से ऊपर उठाएं (घुटना सीधा करें) ।\\\"}\",\"instruction_description_english\":\"{\\\"0\\\":\\\"Lie down with a folded pillow/roller under your exercising side’s knee.\\\",\\\"1\\\":\\\"Tighten the muscles in front of your thigh to press your knee down while simultaneously raising the heel off the ground (straightening the knee).\\\"}\",\"instruction_description_marathi\":null,\"isActive\":1,\"created_at\":\"2022-07-19T03:43:32.000Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2022-07-19T03:43:32.000Z\"}},\"3\":{\"exercise_id\":42,\"exercise_name\":\"Bridging with adductor squeeze\",\"exercise_reps\":10,\"exercise_holds\":\"0\",\"exercise_sets\":2,\"exercise_rests\":30,\"exercise_body_part_id\":8,\"exercise_video_id\":45,\"exercise_instruction_id\":66,\"isActive\":1,\"created_at\":\"2022-07-05T03:44:51.000Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2022-07-05T03:44:51.000Z\",\"exercise_time\":0,\"isMultidirectional\":0,\"isTimeControlled\":0,\"instruction_name\":\"Bridging with adductor squeeze\",\"body_part_name\":\"HIP\",\"video_name\":\"Bridging with adductor squeeze\",\"exercise_days\":29,\"start_date\":\"2022-11-06\",\"end_date\":\"2022-11-06\",\"audioFilePath\":\"/uploads/audios/vedangv7@gmail_com_Bridging with adductor squeeze_November_06_2022_audio.mp3\",\"videoObj\":{\"video_id\":45,\"video_name\":\"Bridging with adductor squeeze\",\"video_type\":\"exercise\",\"video_youtube_id\":\"CamgyVI6-hE\",\"isActive\":1,\"created_at\":\"2022-07-04T05:19:29.000Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2022-07-04T05:19:29.000Z\",\"id\":1},\"instructionObj\":{\"instruction_id\":66,\"instruction_name\":\"Bridging with adductor squeeze\",\"instruction_type\":\"exercise\",\"instruction_description_hindi\":\"{\\\"0\\\":\\\"दोनों घुटनों को मोड़कर पीठ के ब